WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:04.200 --> 00:00:08.200
Disney has done a lot of great things for
popular culture, and touched countless lives

00:00:08.200 --> 00:00:09.200
across the globe.

00:00:09.200 --> 00:00:12.370
Their movies are touted as being wholesome
and full of morality, in addition to being

00:00:12.370 --> 00:00:13.900
fun for the whole family.

00:00:13.900 --> 00:00:17.640
Through the ages, their heroines, heroes,
and villains have been some of the most iconic

00:00:17.640 --> 00:00:19.310
in all of cinematic history.

00:00:19.310 --> 00:00:23.110
But there are some critical eyes out there
too, and some adults aren’t convinced that

00:00:23.110 --> 00:00:26.070
the lessons on the big screen are always the
right ones.

00:00:26.070 --> 00:00:28.680
